If you haven't installed vcpkg yet:
1- git clone https://github.com/microsoft/vcpkg.git
2- cd vcpkg
3- ./bootstrap-vcpkg.bat
4- vcpkg integrate install

Install Ipopt
1- vcpkg install ipopt
2- vcpkg install ipopt:x64-windows
3- add vcpkg/packages/coin-or-ipopt_x64-windows/bin and to the path in environment variable 
3- Go to your project in visual studio 
4- Under C/C++ -> General, add the path to the Ipopt headers (vcpkg/installed/x64-windows/include/coin-or) in the Additional Include Directories section.
5- Under Linker -> General, add the path to the Ipopt library (vcpkg/installed/x64-windows/lib) in the Additional Library Directories section.
6- Under Linker -> Input, add the Ipopt libraries you need (e.g., ipopt.lib) in the Additional Dependencies section.

